{% block content %}

  <article>

    <header class="post-header">
      <div class="post-header-inner">
        <a href="/" class="post-breadcrumb">&larr; Back to Home</a>
        <span class="blog-category">Service</span>
        <h1>Social Media Management for Businesses</h1>
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span>By <strong>Freeland Marketing &amp; Entertainment</strong></span>
          <span>Palm Coast, FL</span>
          <span>Serving Businesses Nationwide</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-featured-img">
      <picture>
        <img src="/blog/images/social-media-management-florida.jpg" alt="Social media management for businesses — professional reviewing analytics dashboard" width="860" height="480" />
      </picture>
    </div>

    <div class="post-body">

      <p>Your business deserves a consistent, professional social media presence — without you spending hours every week writing captions, designing graphics, and figuring out what to post. That is exactly what we do. Freeland Marketing &amp; Entertainment handles your social media end-to-end so you can focus on running your business while we grow your audience.</p>

      <p>We are a nationally operating agency headquartered in Palm Coast, FL — working with businesses across all 50 states. Whether you are in Florida, New York, Texas, or anywhere in between, we bring the same hands-on approach and strategic thinking to every client.</p>

      <h2>What Our Social Media Management Includes</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Custom content creation</strong> — original graphics, captions, Reels scripts, and stories written in your brand voice, powered by our <a href="/services/ai-content-creation/">AI content creation workflows</a></li>
        <li><strong>Content calendar</strong> — a monthly publishing plan built around your services, promotions, and local events</li>
        <li><strong>Consistent scheduling</strong> — 3 to 7 posts per week depending on your package, published at optimal times via <a href="/services/social-media-scheduling/">automated social media scheduling</a></li>
        <li><strong>Community management</strong> — responding to comments, DMs, and reviews professionally and promptly</li>
        <li><strong>Platform optimization</strong> — bio, highlights, link-in-bio, and profile setup dialed in for discovery</li>
        <li><strong>Monthly performance reports</strong> — reach, engagement, follower growth, and website traffic from social</li>
        <li><strong>Strategy calls</strong> — regular check-ins to align content with your current business goals</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Platforms We Manage</h2>

      <p>We focus on the platforms that actually move the needle for businesses:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Instagram</strong> — Feed posts, Reels, and Stories for visual brands and lifestyle-driven audiences</li>
        <li><strong>Facebook</strong> — The highest-reach platform for 35+ demographics and local service businesses</li>
        <li><strong>TikTok</strong> — Short-form video for brands ready to reach younger consumers at scale</li>
        <li><strong>Google Business Profile</strong> — Often overlooked, but posting here directly impacts your local SEO rankings wherever your business operates</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who This Service Is For</h2>

      <p>Our social media management is built for business owners who:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Do not have time to post consistently and know it is costing them customers</li>
        <li>Have tried managing social media themselves but are not seeing results</li>
        <li>Are ready to invest in a consistent brand presence that generates real leads</li>
        <li>Want a dedicated agency — not a faceless national firm — that treats their brand with care</li>
      </ul>

      <p>We have helped restaurants generate same-day reservations, local retailers grow loyal audiences, and service businesses across the country build the kind of social presence that keeps them top of mind when customers are ready to buy.</p>

      <h2>Why Freeland Marketing for Social Media?</h2>

      <p>Kevin personally shows up. For local clients, that means on-location content shoots, real photos and video of your actual business, and content that looks nothing like the generic stock-photo posts your competitors are running. Authenticity drives engagement — and engagement drives customers.</p>

      <p>We also connect your organic social strategy to the bigger picture: <a href="/services/meta-ads/">paid social ads</a> that amplify your best content, <a href="/services/seo/">SEO</a> that builds long-term search visibility, <a href="/services/ai-automation/">AI automation</a> that nurtures the leads your social media generates, and <a href="/services/creative-graphic-design/">professional graphic design</a> that ensures every post matches your brand. Everything works together.</p>

      <div class="post-callout">
        <p>"Our client Tokyo Japanese Steakhouse saw same-day bookings from their first video campaign. Joe Tiki Custom Wood Carving grew 10x in a year. Consistent, strategic social media is the common thread."</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Nationwide Service</h2>

      <p>Headquartered in <strong>Palm Coast, FL</strong> and managing social media for businesses across all 50 states. Every service is delivered remotely — no matter where your business is located.</p>

      <div class="post-cta-box">
        <h3>Get a Free Social Media Audit</h3>
        <p>We review your current profiles, content strategy, and competitive landscape — then show you exactly what is working, what is not, and what a managed approach would look like for your business.</p>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary btn-large">Get My Free Audit &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:2rem;">Want to learn more before reaching out? Read our in-depth guide: <a href="/blog/social-media-management-florida-small-business/">Social Media Management for Small Businesses — What It Costs &amp; What You Get</a>.</p>

